metadata.name: "Girl with a Pearl Earring"
metadata.description:
This is my version of "Girl with a Pearl Earring" by Vermeer, A sweet, deep, sad and unnoticed look that will last all eternity.

Making this piece causes me immense joy, no matter how long you have been an artist, always being able to recognize the work of the great ones before us is an honor and it fills me with pride to show these colors, this big-eyed look based on such great work of the history
